  "title": "urlSync for pages doesn't work with numericSelector and Pagination",
  "body": "Hi\n\nI am trying to implement instantsearch on an app. I have everything work as expected except that the urlSync doesn't work for keeping the current page. It works for everything else and only works as expected when I remove my numericSelectors.\n\nYou can test this by using the tourism example in the docs and enabling urlSync, changing pages and refreshing takes you back to the first page.\n\nAny suggestions?\n",
